    <h2 id="conclusion" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-top: 48px;">Conclusion</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Making trap beats takes practice, but with these fundamentals you can start creating professional-sounding tracks today. Remember:</p>
    <ul style="margin-bottom: 24px; padding-left: 24px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Master the 808 - It's the foundation</li>
